	<p style="margin: 9.75pt 0cm;"><strong>Teacher&rsquo;s Editions</strong><strong></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 9pt 0cm;">The Teacher's Edition for each year level contains the same content as the student book with additional page-by-page wraparound information to assist teachers with lesson planning and instruction. It includes suggestions for integrating key aspects of the curriculum (capabilities, proficiencies, technology, and cross-curriculum priorities) into the teaching of each topic.&nbsp;</p>
